## Why This Is Asked
Webhook security is common in integrations. This question checks practical, end-to-end testing skills for signature validation, payload parsing, replay protection, and rate limiting at a beginner level.

## Key Concepts
- HMAC verification over payload
- Replay protection with nonce/timestamp
- JSON validation and proper error handling
