- Tooling: Postman, curl, pytest, simple in-memory stores

## Code Example
```javascript
const crypto = require('crypto');
function sign(payload, secret){
  const hmac = crypto.createHmac('sha256', secret);
  hmac.update(payload, 'utf8');
  return hmac.digest('hex');
}
```

## Follow-up Questions
- How would you automate replay tests across multiple payloads?
- How would you handle clock skew tolerance and nonce expiry?

